INSTRUCTIONS -->
To Open the Program Install Visual Studio Code .NET SDK And Runtime.
And After that create a folder and put those things in.Then open Visual studio Code and open the folder you created.
Now click on the "Program.cs" file in Visual Studio Code AND FINALLY Go to the toolbar in the bottom of the window, Select Run--> Start Debugging.
From now you should get the program on your Screen
Also make sure to install the official C# Extension From Visual Studio Code's Extension Store before Running the Program 
                                      NOW ENJOY THE STORY!!
